1e3557\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/978289/lifestyle/中醫-藥材-批發-催淚彈-污染-流出市面/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"7月21日的警民衝突期間，警方在上環發射200多發催淚彈，附近除了很多海味舖之外，最多的就是藥材批發店。昨日蔡醫師致電D100節目《左右大局》緊急呼籲，指中醫界收到消息，這一批次的藥材會降價出售予藥材舖及中成藥製藥廠，並相信已有部分流出市面。"},{"pid":"6e081d6186ed751c3900f884fec9e4bf9298de53","tid":1476912,"uid":172290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMdOLK8.gif%5B/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMdOLK8.gif%255B%2F&h=81cb9ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMNsgSe.gif%5B/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMNsgSe.gif%255B%2F&h=4a85a58e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3831819d35ec4fb22c546745d83297ba0535043a","tid":1476912,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c8bab2df5f9e2612ce6e89986e57ac80515c2","tid":1476912,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc052e39005cf414a5a6eb260bb631a4a2214937","tid":1476912,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"記得唔好買"},{"pid":"834bf88d3fc5fdad60c6c6f70c8ae6930e22b1f1","tid":1476912,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"「縮骨、算爆、老撚土」，中哂"},{"pid":"8557307b0